<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="risk-n">risk <strong><em>n</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /rɪsk/    美 /rɪsk/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c-u">1.★ <strong>[C] &amp; [U] 危险；风险：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>increase / reduce the risk</strong> 
增加/降低风险</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Regular exercise cuts the <strong>risk of</strong> heart disease by 50%! 
经常运动可使患心脏病的风险减半！</p><footer>北师大③ – 9</footer></div>

<h4 id="2-c">2.★ <strong>[C] 危险人物；会带来风险的事物：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a major <strong>health / fire risk</strong>
健康/火灾的一大隐患</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="at-risk-from-of">at risk (from / of)</h3>
<p>1.<strong>有危险：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>If we go to war, innocent lives will be <strong>put at risk</strong>. 
如果我们发动战争，无辜的生命就会受到威胁。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The water level has risen so high in several places that many homes are at risk from flooding. 
一些地方水位升高，很多房子都有被洪水淹没的危险。</p><footer>北师大⑧ – 22</footer></div>

<h3 id="at-the-risk-of-doing-sth">at the risk of doing sth</h3>
<p>1.<strong>冒着做某事的风险：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He saved my life at the risk of losing his own. 
他冒着生命危险救了我的命。</p></div>

<h3 id="run-take-a-risk">run / take a risk</h3>
<p>1.<strong>冒险 (run / take risks)：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He felt he had to decide on every step instead of taking risks. 
他觉得他必须考虑好每一步，而不能冒险。</p><footer>人教⑥ – 3</footer></div>

<h3 id="run-take-the-risk-of-doing-sth">run / take the risk of doing sth</h3>
<p>1.<strong>冒险做某事：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Mary couldn’t take the risk of leaving her baby alone even for a short time. 
玛丽不敢冒险让她的孩子独自待着，即使是很短的时间。</p></div></div>